This Navman Move 30 GPS Navigator will get to your destination stress free thanks to features such as advanced lane guidance  live traffic updates and landmark guidance. It is user friendly thanks to its 4.3” touchscreen and intuitive menu.    Stress-Free Navigation  There will be no issues getting to your destination thanks to the array of features on the Navman Move 30 GPS. Advanced Lane Guidance and 3D junction views will ensure you’re in the correct lane ready to turn and will help you to navigate through confusing turns. If you need to get somewhere in a hurry you can always plan your journey just before you leave based on live traffic updates. Alternatively you could use the Smart Route feature which uses historical traffic so you can avoid busy roads during certain times of the day.  Stay Safe on the Road  Going to a new place for the first time can be nerve wracking however the Move 30 GPS Navigator will help keep you safe. It has speed limit alerts to warn you if you’re going over the speed limit  premium safety alerts which warn you of speed or red light cameras as well as school zones which not only helps you to avoid fines  but will keep you alert especially in unfamiliar areas. If it’s a long drive this GPS even has a driver fatigue alert feature!  User Friendly  This GPS has a 4.3” LCD touchscreen is extremely easy to use and the menu is very intuitive. Eliminate stress on the road as this GPS will be able to tell you where everything is. It has 600 000 points of interest stored and has convenient petrol  parking and SOS shortcut buttons to avoid unexpected dilemmas

Features/Description: Purpose built and designed for budding photographers and camera enthusiasts  the 24.2 Mega pixel high performance Nikon D3200 DSLR camera black - Twin Lens Kit comes with a 55 - 300mm lens in addition to its 18 - 55mm lens and utilises the newly developed Nikon DX-format CMOS sensor and EXPEED 3 Image Processing engine and will have you snapping off shots like a professional photographer!    Exceptional Design  The compact and lightweight design of the Nikon D3200 DSLR camera ensures comfortable handling and promotes stable user operation for sharper pictures and minimised blur. Its practical form factor and sensible button layout facilitates excellent portability and ease of operation.  Excellent Still Images  With an effective count of 24.2 mega pixels and an IOS sensitivity range of 100 - 6400  the Nikon D3200 DSLR camera is outfitted with Nikon's DX-format CMOS image sensor and the EXPEED 3 image processing engine. These advanced imaging technologies allow for incredible subject reproduction  expanded dynamic range and improved colour rendering so you'll be able to go on taking outstanding quality pictures with Nikon confidence.  Full High Definition Video Recording  Record and treasure those memorable moments in 1920 x 1080 full high definition resolution at 30fps with the Nikon D3200 DSLR camera  which has been designed to facilitate simple-to-use recording by both budding and experienced photo enthusiasts alike.  3.0in LCD Display  The Nikon D3200 DSLR camera features a brightness adjustable colour TFT LCD type display offers 100% frame coverage and a 160° viewing angle  letting you review your precious photos and videos via the 3.0in viewing area. Now you can always be confident that you've done a perfect job all the time  every time no matter where you are.  Includes 55 - 300mm Lens  This Twin Lens kit includes a 55 - 300mm Lens in addition to the Nikon D3200 DSLR camera's 18 - 55mm Lens  further expanding your photographic possibilities.

Product Name: D5200 DSLR Camera Single Lens 18-55 mm & 55-300 mm VR Lenses Black
Features/Description: The Nikon DS5200 DSLR camera gives you the power to create artistic photos with a range of features to get you there. The Nikon boasts a twin lens kit with 55-200mm range  fantastic 24.1 megapixel resolution  and a range of special effects to take your photography to the next level.    Fantastic Shots  The Nikon camera offers a 39-point Auto Focus system so that you can capture everything in sharp detail  as well as a Scene Recognition System that will help optimize exposure  Auto Focus and white balance.  Adaptive Creativity  Not only does will the Nikon be able to keep up with your still photography needs  but also has Full HD movie recording with a stereo microphone to accurately capture your life and a swivel monitor so you can take a shot regardless of the angle.  Special Effects  Add another degree of creativity to your photos with the Special Effects features  including selective colour  miniature effect  silhouette  night vision  and so on. Let your creativity run free and make your photos different before you even import them to a computer.

Coffee tastes its best when served hot. That's why all professionals work with correctly pre-warmed cups as a matter of principle. If hot coffee is poured into cold porcelain cups  a lot of heat is lost. Too much  in fact. In pre-warmed cups  however  the mouthwatering aroma is released in its entirety. With the elegant  slim cup warmer  JURA offers the ideal accessory for any automatic speciality coffee machine. Two heating elements constantly keep the cups at a temperature of approximately 55°C / 131 °F – ideal for preparing a fiery espresso or a cappuccino topped with milk foam. This makes it an absolute must for all coffee connoisseurs. The slim machine is fitted with a modern cushioning system so that the two drawers close silently. Its capacity is optimally suited to domestic use and cups with a diameter of up to 90 mm / 3.5 inch and up to 110 mm / 4.3 inch tall. Each level provides space for 5 espresso cups (57 mm / 2.2 inch in diameter)  4 coffee cups (66 mm / 2.6 inch) or 6 cappuccino cups (90 mm / 3.5 inch). The closed system prevents valuable heat energy from being lost and the cups from getting dusty. The modern cup warmer proves its eco-intelligence with the programmable automatic switch-on and switch-off time. It can be easily adapted to meet your needs and pre-warms the cups at exactly the right time for when you would like to enjoy your morning coffee. Being eco-friendly has never been so easy.

The Milk Frother is the quick  easy  no-mess way to make perfect  velvety-soft milk foam for cold drinks such as latte frio  cold chocolate and many other popular specialities. Designed in line with JURA's classic style  it's the perfect addition to any coffee machine and an indispensable aid for all lovers of speciality beverages. Easy to operate using a single button  it prepares cold  warm or hot milk foam in a flash.   The perfect recipe for a wide range of speciality drinks  Cold  warm or hot milk foam  Easy one-button operation  High-quality  elegant and easy to clean

The popular speciality coffees of today would be unthinkable without fresh  cold milk. And to make sure this is available whenever it's needed  JURA has further developed the tried-and-tested Cool Control.  The Cool Control cools the milk to as much as 25° below the ambient temperature. Once the temperature reaches 4°C  it is maintained constantly within the optimum range. The Cool Control now comes with an energy-saving automatic switch-off function. When the stainless steel container is removed  the cooling function is automatically deactivated.  The high-quality stainless steel container holds 1 litre. With its bayonet lock  it is easy to remove  open  fill  store in the refrigerator as needed  and clean in the dishwasher.

Go beyond with the Microsoft Surface Pro 2 Tablet  which features a 4th Gen Intel Core i5 Processor  4GB RAM  64GB Storage  a USB 3.0 port  microSDXC reader  Bluetooth and Wi-Fi connectivity  a built-in Kickstand  720p Rear and Front Cameras  a 10.6in ClearType HD Display  an included Surface Pen and Windows 8.1 Pro operating system.    Lasting Performance  The Surface Pro 2 runs on the latest Haswell Core i5-4200U 1.6GHz Processor from Intel for an extra fast tablet which coincides with the 4GB of RAM to give you better multitasking whilst offering up to 10 hours of battery. Running with Windows 8.1 Pro operating system  you can stay updated with apps on the Start screen and add live tiles to fit your needs  with plenty more apps to be discovered in the Windows Store.  Standing Out  The integrated Kickstand gives your Surface Pro 2 stability and flexbility with 2 common positions for best use with a desk or in your lap. Watch your favourite movies and bring your media collection with you thanks to a full-size USB 3.0 port  a microSDXC card reader and Bluetooth 4.0 to make connections with any wireless mice or headsets.  Clearest Viewing  With a 10.6in ClearType HD Display that has wide viewing angles and resolutions of 1920 x 1080  this tablet is optimised for multi-tasking with side-by-side apps as well as auto adjust for screen intensity giving you optimum indoor and outdoor performance. Add this to the inclusion of a 720p Rear and Front Cameras for clear images and photos as well as for video chats.  Work and Play Anywhere  The Surface Pro 2 adds 200GB of SkyDrive storage included for 2 years  so you can store and access your media from anywhere. Turn this tablet into a laptop with Surface Covers that click in and give you the comfort of a regular keyboard in a thin and lightweight design. When closed  the Cover automatically turn off your display and protects it from scratches on the go.  Internet Connection required. Fees and charges may apply

The latest current feedback topology and Marantz own HDAMs are also central to the SR5008. These technologies guarantee both power and detail in your surround sound experience. It also has the networking facilities for gapless HD audio streaming from PC and Android as well as Internet radio  online services and AirPlay from your iPhone  iPad or iPod. And  it includes decoders for standard audio as well as for Dolby TrueHD and DTS-HD Master Audio. The SR5008 also supports Apple lossless  Gapless  FLAC HD 192/24 so you get all the metadata you want. It comes with no less than six HDMI inputs of which one is on the front – making it immediately ready for 3D/4k video and ARC (Audio Return Channel) from ARC-compatible TV sets. Lower resolution video can be up-scaled to 4k too. It easily handles the most demanding of scenes in action films  as well as offering excellentquality music playback - thanks to the latest Marantz audio technologies and 180W from the 7 amplifiers. Everything sounds clear  detailed  and alive with this set. To finish off  the SR5008 comes with a whole range of convenience features such as: Setup Assistant  auto calibration with Audyssey MultiEQ XT and Dynamic Volume Control; Multi-Room with multi-source flexibility; and video-off mode to ensure that you enjoy your music and movies in true dynamic Marantz style. It also has the specially developed Marantz Remote App for iPhone and Android devices. All of which makes the SR5008 a true combination of style  power and ease.  • 7ch discrete power amplifier  180 W per channel • Current Feedback circuitry with Marantz HDAM • DLNA1.5 Network audio streaming and Internet radio • MP3  WAV  AAC  FLAC  WMA  Lossless  FLAC192/24 (HD) • Gapless Playback • Spotify  last.fm  Flickr  Internet Radio support • Apple AirPlay and Windows 8/RT compatible • Audyssey MultEQ XT  Dynamic EQ and Dynamic Volume • 6+1in / 1out HDMI (3D/ARC/CEC/4K) • Full 4k compatibility – Scaling – Pass through – GUI overlay • Analogue & HDMI Upconversion to 4k • Multilingual Setup Assistant and Audyssey calibration makes hook up an easy

7-channel amplifier  110 watts per channel into 8 ohms (20-20 000 Hz) at 0.08% THD  with 2 channels driven  Dolby and DTS surround sound decoding  including Dolby Pro Logic IIz and DTS Neo:X  analog-to-HDMI video upconversion (up to 1080p and 4K)  Audyssey Laboratories' MultEQ XT six-point auto setup and room calibration system (microphone included)  Audyssey DSX processing for enhanced surround sound height or width effects using additional front speakers  Audyssey Dynamic Volume mode to keep listening levels steady  Audyssey Dynamic EQ for fuller sound at lower listening levels

Air Command - Hover the S Pen over the screen and simply press the pen button to instantly access 5 useful S Pen features: Action Memo turn your handwritten memos into actionable links: calls  new contacts  To-Dos or emails  web or location searches  tasks. For example  write down a telephone number  press Link to Action  and you can call that number directly without any additional steps. Scrapbook GALAXY Note 3 allows you to track down and categorize images  videos and other contents by tapping the 'Scrapbooker' button in Air Command. Just circle the information or image that you want to save and move it into Scrapbook. It's easy to categorize and design your own personalized Scrapbook. S Finder you can search your entire phone from hand-written memos to the web. Simply click the pen to access S Finder and then search by keywords and/or apply date  location or content filters from one starting point to find related images  videos  music  personal notes  documents  events or chats  even Help advice. It’s easy with automatically saved dates and enabled location tags in the Camera  S Note  Scrapbook  Voice recorder. The new S Note lets you quickly scribble notes on extensive canvases  browse through them almost effortlessly and edit them beautifully. The new S Note can also be synced with Evernote or a Samsung account to enable viewing from your compatible PC or tablets. The Easy Chart function also transforms scribbled charts into professional-looking graphs instantly. New Easy Clip Select the area to be cropped  and the new Easy Clip will remove the background instantly Enhance the boundaries of your creativity with the new Easy Clip. Direct Pen Input The GALAXY Note 3 recognizes both your handwriting and typing. The advanced handwriting recognition technology  helps to accurately read most writing styles and be transcribed  into a message  planner  alarm or phone function. This feature allows you to experience great versatility and flexibility.

Product Name: Samsung Galaxy Gear Watch - Wht Gold
Features/Description: Call - Missed a call because you couldn't hear or reach your phone? Now  with GALAXY Gear  never miss a call; you can answer and make calls from your wrist. S Voice GALAXY Gear is set to respond to your fingers or voice at all times. The S voice function lets GALAXY Gear assist your busy on-the-go life by allowing you to create schedules and check new messages instantly. Notification & Smart Relay Experience seamless communication from your Gear to your phone. When you get an important notification on GALAXY Gear  your phone will automatically show the message by picking up the phone. Enjoy the delightful communication without the hassle of any additional steps. Memographer Missed an important moment while setting up your camera phone? Now with GALAXY Gear  you can take a quick snapshot memo or catch a treasured image before the perfect moment passes. And of course  Gear lets you share these memos instantly through SNS. Voice Memo Tell GALAXY Gear everything you want to remember. You no longer need to take your phone out of your pocket or bag to write a memo. Just speak to your Gear.

Product Name: Polar FT60 Heart Rate Monitor Woman's Lilac
Features/Description: The FT60 also comes with the comfortable Wearlink Coded Transmitter which has user replaceable batteries  (we recommend changing these every 12 months). The FT60 is able to store up to 99 exercise files  and with the use of the Flowlink device  data stored on the watch can be uploaded to Polar’s FREE online software. The Flowlink is not included with the FT60 but is available under our accessory section. Where the FT60 stands out  is with the Polar STAR Training Program. This program allows you to set a goal  and the watch will provide you with weekly targets to reach. The targets are based on spending a certain amount of time in 3 different heart rate zones. If you are successful with completing the weekly targets without over or under training  the program will change. The FT60 also includes the Polar Fitness Test  which helps provide an approx VO2max. This figure allows for a greater accuracy when calculating calorie expenditure.     Exercise summary showing duration of workout  maximum and average heart rate for the session  time spent in heart rate zone and calories burned. Fitness is about more than just exercise  so get the whole picture with this Black Flex Wireless Activity Wristband from Fitbit. It tracks a wide range of things  from calories burned to hours slept  so you can stay informed about your body and keep up with your fitness goals.   Multi-Tracking  This Flex wristband tracks all kinds of data about your fitness  including steps taken  calories burned  distance travelled  active minutes  hours slept and even the quality of your sleep. It helps you get the full picture when it comes to your body.  Stats Syncing  It couldn’t be easier to sync the data collected by this wireless activity wristband with your iPhone  Android device or computer. Simply copy your stats across via Bluetooth and you can review your stats whenever or wherever you want.  Set Goals  Complete the goals you set by staying up to date using this Fitbit wristband. It allows you to set fitness goals for the day and then will update you on your progress via a simple LED light system – so it’s easy to see at a glance how much you’ve done.  Simple Tough Design  The Flex has a simple design that won’t get in the way or be too bulky  keeping it simple and sleek so you can forget you’re even wearing it. The Flex is also water-resistant and has a silent wake up alarm - making it easier for you to get up in time for your morning run.

Product Name: Jawbone UP Wristband in Black - Large
Features/Description: Wristband towards a healthier lifestyle - UP intelligently tracks hours slept  light vs. deep sleep and waking moments. It also tracks the distance covered  calories burned  active time  activity intensity. It even reminds you to move when you've been inactive for too long. The UP wristband lasts up to 10 days when fully charged. The Smart Alarm helps you wake up feeling refreshed-at the right moment in your sleep cycle.
